name: What is not called
description:
ES: /En la cueva susurré su nombre: ucumar. Las sílabas, desiguales, se distribuyeron entre las piedras. 'Tengo miedo'. Se oyó una mano moverse y dijo: 'de eso se trata'./ 

escultura en plástico y yeso + fotogrametría + intervención gráfica


EN: /In the cave I whispered his name: ucumar. The syllables, uneven, were distributed among the stones. 'I'm scared'. A moving hand was heard. He said: 'that's what it's all about'./

plastic and plaster sculpture + photogrammetry + graphic intervention
